Chojnowo  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Tolkmicko, within Elbląg County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  east of Tolkmicko,  north-east of Elbląg, and  north-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
